trans-unit.source: The ImageCodecInfo class provides the necessary storage members and methods to retrieve all pertinent information about the installed image encoders and decoders (called codecs).
trans-unit.target: Klassen ImageCodecInfo gir nødvendig lagring medlemmer og metoder for å hente all relevant informasjon om installert bildet kodere og dekodere (kalt kodeker).

trans-unit.source: Not inheritable.
trans-unit.target: Ikke arvbare.

trans-unit.source: GDI+ uses image encoders to convert the images stored in <xref:System.Drawing.Bitmap> objects to various file formats.
trans-unit.target: GDI + bruker bildet kodere til å konvertere bildene i <xref:System.Drawing.Bitmap>objekter i ulike filformater.</xref:System.Drawing.Bitmap>

trans-unit.source: Image encoders are built into GDI+ for the BMP, JPEG, GIF, TIFF, and PNG formats.
trans-unit.target: Bilde kodere er innebygd i GDI + for BMP, JPEG, GIF, TIFF og PNG-format.

trans-unit.source: An encoder is invoked when you call the <xref:System.Drawing.Image.Save%2A> or <xref:System.Drawing.Image.SaveAdd%2A> method of a <xref:System.Drawing.Image> object.
trans-unit.target: En koder aktiveres når du kaller den <xref:System.Drawing.Image.Save%2A>eller <xref:System.Drawing.Image.SaveAdd%2A>-metoden til et <xref:System.Drawing.Image>objektet.</xref:System.Drawing.Image> </xref:System.Drawing.Image.SaveAdd%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Image.Save%2A>
